**Laboratory Features:**
- Fully equipped Chemistry, Physics, and Biology sections
- Digital microscopes with projection capabilities
- Computerized data collection and analysis systems
- Safety-first design with modern ventilation and emergency systems
- Capacity for 40 students per session
- Dedicated research area for advanced projects

